<item>
		<title>As Iraqi forces fight to take Mosul, car bomb in Baghdad kills 23 people</title>


		<description>MOSUL, Iraq (Reuters) - Islamic State militants captured an Iraqi police colonel and eight other officers on Monday after they ran out of ammunition during a skirmish in the battle for western Mosul, an Iraqi Interior Ministry official said.&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
